13
00:01:17,625 --> 00:01:20,750
<i>The thing is, if Rodrick would
just take me under his wing,</i>

14
00:01:20,833 --> 00:01:22,666
<i>I could totally surprise him.</i>

15
00:01:22,750 --> 00:01:24,875
