change things for us.</i>

16
00:01:24,958 --> 00:01:28,250
[crowd cheers]

17
00:01:28,833 --> 00:01:31,416
<i>But I guess that's
just not gonna happen.</i>

18
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:33,416
<i>And before long,
Rodrick will move out,</i>

19
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:35,708
<i>and I'll have to figure
things out for myself.</i>

20
00:01:36,750 --> 00:01:38,375
[coughs]

21
00:01:38,458 --> 00:01:39,666
[both snoring]

22
00:01:39,750 --> 00:01:42,625
<i>But as long as the two of us
are living under the same roof,</i>

23
00:01:42,708 --> 00:01:45,833
<i>I'm gonna soak up every bit of
big brother knowledge I can get.</i>

24
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:53,833
