dishes away before we get back.

33
00:02:16,125 --> 00:02:18,125
Okay, yeah. I got your
hair dryer and my belt.

34
00:02:18,208 --> 00:02:20,568
Um, was that... Was... [stammers]
Am I forgetting something?

35
00:02:21,250 --> 00:02:22,666
Your pants?

36
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:25,333
Right. My pants.

37
00:02:26,166 --> 00:02:28,041
