224
00:12:10,458 --> 00:12:14,583
and if I miss two in a row,
Miss Tilly's gonna be mad.

225
00:12:14,666 --> 00:12:17,166
Relax, Rowley. I've got
everything under control.

226
00:12:18,041 --> 00:12:19,041
Hmm.

227
00:12:21,958 --> 00:12:24,916
