there? Are they… partying?

231
00:12:43,416 --> 00:12:47,000
[Greg] I think I can
reach the lock. [grunting]

232
00:12:48,416 --> 00:12:49,583
[Rowley grunts] Ow!

233
00:12:51,083 --> 00:12:52,500
[sighs]

234
00:12:53,666 --> 00:12:55,000
Can you reach it?

235
00:12:55,083 --> 00:12:56,083
No.

236
00:12:56,166 --> 00:12:59,833
But I've got an idea. Wait here.

237
00:13:02,458 --> 00:13:04,125
[rock music playing]

238
00:13:04,208 --> 00:13:06,000
Let's get this party started!

239
00:13:06,083 --> 00:13:07,500
[cheering, laughing]

240
00:13:07,583 --> 00:13:09,916
- Whoo!
- [teenager] Nice brain bucket.

241
00:13:11,500 --> 00:13:13,642
And I was like, "Underwear
goes under your pants, bro."

