Well, I figured you might know
some trick. Some way out of this.

825
00:44:13,291 --> 00:44:16,333
Well, you could pretend
you're sick. Skip school.

826
00:44:16,416 --> 00:44:19,375
Mom would know I'm
faking. She always knows.

827
00:44:19,458 --> 00:44:21,291
You could tell your
teacher Manny ate it.

828
00:44:21,375 --> 00:44:23,625
Really, Rodrick? That's the
best you can come up with?

829
00:44:29,208 --> 00:44:32,958
You know I still have dirt on you,
