843
00:45:13,166 --> 00:45:14,666
I want cash.

844
00:45:14,750 --> 00:45:17,000
[groans] I don't have any cash.

845
00:45:17,083 --> 00:45:19,791
I'm talking Mom Bucks.
Large bills only.

846
00:45:19,875 --> 00:45:21,791
Come on, Rodrick.
Don't you have enough?

847
00:45:21,875 --> 00:45:25,625
No, you can never have enough Mom
Bucks. That's Rodrick Rule number five.

848
00:45:25,708 --> 00:45:27,833
Fine. I'll give you
20. That's fair.

849
00:45:28,833 --> 00:45:33,666
Mmm, actually, you seem
a little too eager.

850
00:45:33,750 --> 00:45:34,958
Make it a hundred.

851
00:45:35,041 --> 00:45:36,041
[groans]

852
00:45:37,333 --> 00:45:39,833
Fine. But you can't
tell anyone about this.

853
00:45:40,583 --> 00:45:44,583
I may be a lot of things, but
one thing I am not is a snitch.

854
00:45:48,500 --> 00:45:50,750
