913
00:49:16,333 --> 00:49:19,017
Didn't I tell you it wasn't a good
idea for these two to be hanging out?

914
00:49:19,041 --> 00:49:24,041
Greg, it might not have been your
party, but you helped cover it up.

915
00:49:24,125 --> 00:49:26,041
You lied to us.

916
00:49:26,125 --> 00:49:27,791
And because of that,
you are grounded.

917
00:49:27,875 --> 00:49:31,166
No video games or
electronics for three weeks.

918
00:49:31,250 --> 00:49:33,625
And Rodrick, you're
the older brother.

919
00:49:33,708 --> 00:49:36,208
What kind of example are
you setting for Greg?

920
00:49:36,291 --> 00:49:39,333
A bad example?

921
00:49:40,416 --> 00:49:44,041
